originalText: Excuse me $(#sir/ma'am), I'm busy making men out of these dirtbags.
Are you all deaf? I told you to train like men - not like little girls!
You over there! Stop standing around and do as I ordered you! Do you understand me, dirtbag!
Holy mother of dirtbags, you truly are a miserable, miserable sight to behold!
You are all a bunch of pathetic dirtbags! Even if I brought the oldest, weakest zoner in here, he'd do better than you!
...Twenty-one, twenty-two... Wrong, bad form! Start all over! One, two, three, four...
You over there! Recruit! Is my yelling distracting you!? WELL, THAT'S TOO BAD!
So you want to protect Core City civilians, right? ::Laughs.:: Right now you wouldn't even be able to protect your miserable butts from a single braindead rathound!
You, over there, recruit! Recruit! Why in the sweet mother of dirtbags are you caressing that punching bag!? What's next? A massage!?
I thought I said fifty push-ups, not five and let-me-do-the-other-fourty-five-wrong! Again!
You all think you're "hardcore," think you're "dominating"? ::Laughs.::
You're gonna train until you turn into a puddle of sweat.
